         <abstract>
            <p>We study the imaginary quadratic fields such that the Iwasawa λ&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt;-invariant equals 1, obtaining information on zeros of 2-adic L-functions and relating this to congruences for fundamental units and class numbers.</p>
          </abstract>
